<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">Last updated: February 19, 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            TopClanker is a static informational website. We don't collect, store, or process any personal information from our visitors.
            No accounts, no logins, no tracking cookies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> - Displays ads on our site. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your visits to this and other sites.</li>
            <li><strong>Netlify</strong> - Hosts and serves our website.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            TopClanker doesn't set our own cookies. Google AdSense may set cookies for ad personalization and measurement.
            You can opt out of personalized ads at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google Ad Settings</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Data We Don't Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We don't collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Email addresses</li>
            <li>IP addresses (beyond basic server logs)</li>
            <li>Search history</li>
            <li>User accounts</li>
            <li>Form submissions</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">External Links</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Our site links to third-party websites (model providers, benchmark sources). We're not responsible for their privacy practices.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            We may update this policy. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:rankings@topclanker.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">rankings@topclanker.com</a>
        </p>
